# thaibraille
Thai Braille for Natural Language Processing.

## Install

> pip install thaibraille

## Usage

**Thai word to braille**

```python
from thaibraille import thai_word_braille

print(thai_word_braille("แมว"))

# output: ⠣⠍⠺
```

This function support Thai and number only.

